WEBVTT

00:03.036 --> 00:05.771
ANNOUNCER:
<i>This is the story of two sisters,</i>

00:05.772 --> 00:07.840
<i>Jessica Tate</i>

00:07.841 --> 00:10.309
<i>and Mary Campbell.</i>

00:10.310 --> 00:13.812
<i>These are the Tates,</i>

00:13.813 --> 00:17.616
<i>and these are the Campbells.</i>

00:17.617 --> 00:20.185
<i>And this is</i> Soap.

00:20.186 --> 00:22.688
[ALL CLAMORING]

00:24.000 --> 00:30.074
